{"tid":327023,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"職業無分貴賤？我呸！","createTime":"2017-07-18T12:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T10:07:08.000Z","uid":40938,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3070bce8dbfbf5d87f9fc6188798fbe7c1c1c79c","tid":327023,"uid":40938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:29:08.000Z","msg":"我同你地講！有啲職業就係高尚，有啲職業就係賤，點會冇分別？ 高尚有醫生，清潔工，地盤佬，冇左呢啲人我地都會收皮，呢啲職業除左搵食仲真係服務緊社會。我特別尊重地盤佬，真漢子！經過過地盤就知幾辛苦環境幾惡劣，又危險，真係搵命搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁邊啲賤？我估大家都心中有數，呢啲人我地冇左佢唔會收皮，仲反而少左騷擾清靜左！就係你班垃圾基金保險佬！！屌晒你地老尾，講真自己做緊呢啲職業好應該差恥，晚晚應該屌自己一次先訓！學歴高底唔重要，唔應該受歧視，但你都可以選擇高尚既地盤佬，或者賤過狗既基金保險佬 著曬老西蠟晒頭唔代表唔賤架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重申一次！職業有分貴賤！"},{"pid":"e0fa9fe92e3c2ab9a0ca698049245ccc896cb852","tid":327023,"uid":12085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"地盤佬先係上等人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb5b79e4c370f2ce0b4e128b25875677f6dd060","tid":327023,"uid":40938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地盤佬先係上等人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真 最尊敬佢地"},{"pid":"7838b6999c519724762af39bdf2490a957ebf95c","tid":327023,"uid":53619,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:34:53.000Z","msg":"讀唔成書學人戴光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116679184416ef4b0fc8a5300959b360c72f302b","tid":327023,"uid":36049,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"呢句野係成功人士安慰垃圾既說話😂😂😂"},{"pid":"32cdb97145c88abc7638b6608612d4e32710bb17","tid":327023,"uid":106149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:41:37.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b5143245d3e92d7a68fd28a5dc570c2c4d87b3","tid":3270